title: login error can someone help please
body: for some reason i can connect to the north america server but not ocenia it just says did not receive a response from server and attempts 3 times and goes login error the server status says everythings online but im confused why north america works normal but not my server please help

replies.body:
Hey ThanhOii69,

Riot is aware of the issue and is working to resolve it as soon as possible. Check out the announcement by Agent Mindstar below:
